{"tid":1485770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下次試下唔好再用有鬼論","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T19:50:11.000Z","uid":210636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be5eb123510df5e327e7f5357bb0e647aca97fa0","tid":1485770,"uid":210636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有小小野想講，「核彈都唔割」嘅覺悟，唔係一句口號，而係比你想像中更難做到的事，因為背後係我地未必認同個決定，但會理解，就算你唔認同，都大可以未去到割，我哋知道我哋係同一個群體之下，無人可以確定每個決定都唔柒，但我地肯一齊孭飛，唔認同對方，都唔撚好用有鬼論啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n818有好多人都會話返屋企，我都好撚認同，但面對入夜仲留守緊嘅人，我們就劃上佢地等於鬼亦不合理，我地已經冇野可以再輸，更加唔好太沉迷捉鬼遊戲，港共政權其中一樣可恥在於瓦解人與人之間信任，要好好相信每個手足都有獨立思考包括前線。<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><em><em><em><em><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>[b]我地用道理互相說服，唔好再用有鬼論啊，屌</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></em></em></em></em></strong></strong></strong></strong></span>[/b<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\